        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Another exciting addition is the ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Voice Design",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " tool, which allows you to craft entirely new voices from scratch. You can adjust parameters like age, gender, and accent to create characters for games or animations. I designed a quirky narrator for a kids’ series, and it added so much personality to the project.",
